bcunit
------------------------------------------
This is BCUnit, a fork of the defunct project CUnit, with several fixes and
patches applied.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.1-1
  libbcunit-devel-5.4.17-1bl1
  libbcunit1-5.4.17-1bl1
  libncursesw10-6.5+20240427-1
  pkg-config-2.4.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.44-1
  cmake-3.28.3-1
  cygport-0.36.9-1
  gcc-core-12.4.0-3
  gcc-g++-12.4.0-3
  libncurses-devel-6.5+20240427-1
  ninja-1.12.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bcunit

Canonical download:
  https://gitlab.linphone.org/BC/public/bcunit/-/archive/5.4.17/bcunit-5.4.17.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack bcunit-5.4.17-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./bcunit-5.4.17-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/bcunit-5.4.17-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/bcunit-5.4.17-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbcunit1-5.4.17-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libbcunit-devel-5.4.17-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

